column5: thanks for the read.  some great fish there!
Slobby lakers, log pike and football smallies... three species to easily fall in love with the chase Steve.  Great season again!
Well done Steve. I might have to start ice fishing this year !
Outstanding season for ya! I checked out your laker top 5 lures video; great stuff man. I will definitely try a couple of your favorites this winter!
those are some chunky lakers, great season recap as always
this guy taking my fishing and putting it to shame. You are absolutely killing 3 of the species that i absolutely love to chase. unreal.  What was the weight on that one absolutely slob smallie?

this guy taking my fishing and putting it to shame. You are absolutely killing 3 of the species that i absolutely love to chase. unreal.  What was the weight on that one absolutely slob smallie? There's a few. I had 4 over 7 this season. Biggest was the second from the bottom was 7-10

There's a few. I had 4 over 7 this season. Biggest was the second from the bottom was 7-10  that is insane  i spend a lot of time fishing smallies and have yet to run into a fish even close to 7...i guess im just fishing the wrong water lol
